subproject.description: 1) For the exit strategy, UNDP had facilitated the development of ATSEA project proposal submitted to GEF focusing on International Waters (IW) issue. 2) In line with this, the administration and operations of ATSEF were transferred to ATSEF Secretariat located in the Agency for Marine Affairs and Fisheries Research (AMFR/BRKP). 3) Further operations will be under the AMFR together with its day-to-day operations of the office and ATSEF Regional Office which had been supported by the Australian government.
subproject.title: ATSEF
